message: switched sphinx theme to alabaster with MDAnalysis styling
Universe now works with StringIO objects (#1254)
changes string.uppercase to string.ascii_uppercase for py3 compatibility (#1309)
Residues with the same residue ids are not merged by default (#1307)
Fix doc warnings in MDAnalysis package
wateranalysis: Fixed case when no water molecules in selection.
Changed dt to include step in Universe.transfer_to_memory() (#1321)
Fix hbond cannot deal with atoms too far (PR #1325)
Fix #1324 (encore required reader with timeseries capabilities)
fixed remaining sphinx warnings and doc touchups
sphinx: make sphinx fail on warnings and be verbose (local sphinx Makefile)
Fix small rendering errors in the doc

Fixes Issue 1331 This handles the case where number of items is exactly divisible by number of items per line. Previously the code would always round up  where instead it should only round up when not exactly divisible.
changed OAuth token for doc deployment from Travis CI (#1338)
fix start  stop  step values of AnalysisBase (#1340)
hbond analysis: fixed incorrect residue handling with trailing numbers (#1339)
added OC1 and OC2 to default list of hydrogen bond acceptors
changed URL for docs to new http://docs.mdanalysis.org
Use Timestep API more in reader speed boost
